08/John-Lydon-and-Patti-Smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/John-Lydon-and-Patti-Smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/John-Lydon-and-Patti-Smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/John-Lydon-and-Patti-Smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/John-Lydon-and-Patti-Smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/john-lydon">约翰·莱登 (John Lydon)</a>表示，他认为将朋克的起源归功于<a href="/artists/patti-smith">帕蒂·史密斯 (Patti Smith)</a>以及更广泛的纽约，是“错误的”——他说英国首先做到了这一点。</p><p>史密斯凭借 1975 年的首张专辑“Horses”成为美国朋克运动的重要组成部分。然而，这位前<a href="/artists/sex-pistols">Sex Pistol</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/public-image-ltd">Public Image Ltd</a>主唱声称，英国才是该流派的真正发源地，拥有<a href="/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a> 、 <a href="/artists/t-rex">T-Rex</a> 、Sweet、 <a href="/artists/the-clash">The Clash</a> 、The Dammed 和 Sex Pistols 等乐队。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/23439030/john-lydon-grief-wife-nora-sex-pistols-court-feud/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《太阳报》</em></a>采访时，莱登说：“我听到很多美国记者假装整个朋克的影响力都来自纽约。嗯，你好？像 Sweet 的《Ballroom Blitz》和 Mud 的《Tiger Feet》这样的乐队——就是这么做的，伙计！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CvzcE8-JIWz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-